# Boston PHP
## Turbo-charge your web app with client side templates (and render your views in any language too)!

Building super-responsive apps that work on multiple platforms is more important than ever. I'll show you how to use Mustache templates, AJAX and JSON to increase the response time and reduce bandwidth and requests to your server. 

## Demo

http://adrane.com/templates/

Use the arrow keys, or click next and previous to get the pages with AJAX and render client-side. Click the other menu items to get them with regular request.